                    ...0 .... = Admission Control Mandatory: No
                    .... 0010 = AIFSN: 2
                    0... .... = Reserved: 0
                ECW: 0x32
                    0011 .... = ECW Max: 3
                    .... 0010 = ECW Min: 2
                TXOP Limit: 47
